</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_537" id="267v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_537_r1l20">Gemeiner Reıchs Stette <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> botten der <expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynung</expan> ın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_537_r1l21">ſwoben als ſıe nehſt ʒu Vlme bey eın <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn </ab>
</div>
